NORTH ATLANTIC.
BERMUDA TO AZORES.
122 FOOT M/V ZEEPAARD, SEVEN PERSONS ON BOARD, OVERDUE
BERMUDA (32-20N 064-44W) TO AZORES (37-44N 025-40W).

LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO RCC NORFOLK,
